    </div>
    
</div>

<div class="nav-menu">
    
</div>

    <!-- Main Block (Scroll Container) -->
    <main data-scroll-container data-barba="container" data-barba-namespace="about">

        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <section class="hero">

            <!-- Background Video -->
            <div class="hero__background">
                <img src="/img/about-background.jpg" alt="Disney Castle, Universal Studios Sign, and downtown orlando">
            </div>

            <!-- Content -->
            <div class="hero__content">

                <h1>Our heart is in <span>Orlando</span></h1>
                <h4>The city beautiful</h4>
                
            </div>

        </section>

        <!-- Family Section -->
        <section class="section">

             <!-- Content Block -->
             <div class="content xl">
                <h2><span>Family</span> owned &amp; operated.</h2>
                <p>We are a family owned & operated business centered in Orlando, Florida. This company was founded in 2013 by Beatriz Murillo and Juan Lopez, with the core goal of providing first class black car services around the Orlando and Tampa Bay areas. We have since then grew and now offer long distance rides throughout the state of Florida.</p>
            </div>

        </section>

        <!-- Professional & Friendly Service -->
        <section class="friendly">
            <div class="friendly__map">
                <img src="/img/friendly.png" alt="Man wearing a hat and smiling in black and white">
            </div>

            <div class="friendly__content">
                <div class="content">
                    <h2 class="white">Always <span>professional.</span> Always <span>friendly.</span></h2>
                    <p>We are always professional and always courteous. When travelling with us, you will never encounter a rude driver or recive subpar service. We take pride in what we do and love meeting new people. The first thing you will see when our driver arrives is a smile on their face, because it truly is our pleasure to serve you.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Quality Section -->
        <section class="section">

            <!-- Content Block -->
            <div class="content xl">
               <h2>We’re driven by <span>quality</span></h2>
               
                    <p>We believe in going the extra mile for you. When you ride with us, you can expect only the highest caliber of service. We make sure that we arrive to your pick up point early and get you to your destination in a timely manner so you never have to wait a minute.</p>
                
                    <p>Quality means driving safely so that you have the ultimate peace of mind and can relax knowing that you are in good hands. We also have child seats to accommodate your young ones and keep them safe.</p>
                
                    <p>We also take the time to clean our vehicles both before and after every ride so that you can travel in a clean and sanitary enviornment. This is more important than ever due to COVID-19, so you can relax knowing that we are doing our part.</p>
                
           </div>

       </section>

       <!-- Quote Section -->
       <section class="quote">
           <div class="quote__background">
                <img src="/img/quote.jpg" alt="Car driving at night with blurred lights">
           </div>

           <div class="quote__content">
               <h2 class="white">Quality means doing it right when no one is looking.</h2>
               <h3 class="white light">&dash; Henry Ford</h3>
           </div>
       </section>

        <!-- Reviews  -->
        <div id="reviews-react-app"></div>

        <!-- Call To Action -->
        <section class="cta">
    <div class="cta__card">
        <div class="content">
            <h2 class="white">Book a <span>ride with us.</span></h2>
            <p>Ready to book a ride for your next trip to Orlando? You can book your ride online using our online booking system. You will be able to complete the entire booking process online so that when it’s timefor your ride its effortless.</p>
            <a href="#content" class="btn-pill filled primary">Book Reservation </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

        <!-- Our Fleet -->
        <section class="section">

    <!-- Section Grid -->
    <div class="section__grid">

        <!-- Content Block -->
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Check out our <span>fleet.</span></h2>
            <p>Take a look at our fleet of vehicles and see which of our vehicles will best accommodate your needs.</p>
            <a href="/fleet" class="btn-pill hollow dark">View Fleet </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Image -->
        <div class="section__image">
            <picture>
                <source srcset="/img/fleet.webp" type="image/webp">
                <source srcset="/img/fleet.png" type="image/png">
                <img src="/img/fleet.png" alt="Mercedes car coming out of a circle">
            </picture>
        </div>

    </div>

</section>

        <!-- Contact Us -->
        <section id="contact" class="contact">
    <div class="contact__image">
        <picture>
            <source srcset="/img/contact.webp" type="image/webp">
            <source srcset="/img/contact.jpg" type="image/jpeg">
            <img src="/img/contact.jpg" alt="Mercedes car coming out of a circle">
        </picture>
    </div>
    <div class="contact__card">
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Have a question? <span>Contact us.</span></h2>
            <p>We’re happy to help you. Please feel free to give us a call or send us an email and we will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
            <a class="contact__method" href="m&#97;i&#108;&#116;o&#58;&#104;e&#108;lo&#64;un%&#54;9&#116;ed&#116;&#37;72%&#54;1&#118;e&#108;&#46;llc" >
                <svg><use href="/img/icons.svg#email"></use></svg>
                <h5>hello@unitedtravel.llc</h5>
            </a>
            <a class="contact__method" href="tel:123-456-7890">
                <svg><use href="/img/icons.svg#iphone"></use></svg>
                <h5>(123) 456-7890</h5>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

        
